{"tid":864363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國揚言嚴懲 沙地威脅動用「石油武器」  油價恐漲至200美元","createTime":"2018-10-16T06:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T12:54:51.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"9666b0c079ebdfc1acc50e76a20a4ca40d7b6eb1","tid":864363,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T06:52:13.000Z","msg":"沙地阿拉伯記者卡舒吉(Jamal Khashoggi)失蹤案，令美國與沙地的關係驟然緊張。沙地官方媒體威脅動用「石油武器」，讓油價漲至每桶100至200美元，甚至再翻一倍。<br />\n <br />\n沙地官媒阿拉伯衞星電視台(Al Arabiya TV)總經理Turki Aldakhil在其網站撰文稱，如果美國對沙地實施制裁，油價可能會漲至每桶200美元，甚至更高，並將嚴重衝擊全球經濟。<br />\n<br />\n外電較早時報道，對於《華盛頓郵報》特約記者卡舒吉失蹤一事，美國總統特朗普揚言，若證實沙地為幕後黑手，將對沙地作出嚴懲。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普其後在社交網站發文表示，與沙地國王薩勒曼(King Salman)通電話，對方否認知悉沙地記者事件，並正與土耳其就事件密切合作，特朗普將派遣國務卿蓬佩奧會見沙地國王。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/current/article/1967793/美國揚言嚴懲+沙地官媒%3A油價恐漲至200美元\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1967793%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%8F%9A%E8%A8%80%E5%9A%B4%E6%87%B2%2B%E6%B2%99%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%98%E5%AA%92%253A%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E6%81%90%E6%BC%B2%E8%87%B3200%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83&d=EhBP80KDfqtSfCVNn%2BWU%2FhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=8dad1a23\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/current/article/1967793/美國揚言嚴懲+沙地官媒%3A油價恐漲至200美元</a><br />\n<br />\n香港有冇影響？"},{"pid":"6addddaa83a78bffa05aa019de1789ebf9ce9cce","tid":864363,"uid":216709,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:05:05.000Z","msg":"入定貨等升"},{"pid":"4d0a9630cf60627191da1be7aaca1998fdf461f3","tid":864363,"uid":2429,"like":53,"dislike":2,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:07:51.000Z","msg":"想變委內瑞拉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5e42e0b2d84ff1b0c1688a8ed5b29d185f15ee","tid":864363,"uid":161098,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:09:44.000Z","msg":"咁tesla股價會升"},{"pid":"67ca9b4d4d829c645dbb4496be6b3e7c52936370","tid":864363,"uid"